Overload.descr:
Displays a choose box with the given "title" and containing items with the strings "item1", etc. 
If the user chooses an object, var will be updated to contain the number of the selected object (an integer, 1, 2, 3, …); 
otherwise, stores zero in var if the user exits without choosing. Returns true (non zero) if the user selects an object, otherwise returns false (0).

